      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's not even about being imperfect though. it's just... the effort of it all. every single day is just a performance. i'm constantly calculating how to act, how to speak, how to not seem \"weird.\" it's like i'm running a marathon just to stay at the starting line. everything feels so heavy and pointless. like why even keep doing this if it never actually gets easier?",
